This directory's purpose is to perform Virtual Screening using Autodock Vina [1] and MGLTools [2], by using Python scripts.

The scripts are described below:

* zinc_db.py
This file decomposes a single .mol2 file into several .mol2 files.

* prepare_ligand.py
This file converts the .mol2 files into .pdbqt files.

* prepare_receptor.py
This file converts the .pdb files into .pdbqt files.

* vs_main.py
This is the file that actually performs the Virtual Screening.

* vina.py
Contains functions used by AutoDock Vina.

* mol2.py
Contains functions used to manipulate .mol2 files.

* analysis directory
Contains scripts for a brief analysis of the results obtained from the Virtual Screening.




